<appendix id="app.deployment.docupdates">
 <title>Documentation Updates</title>
 <para>
  This chapter lists content changes for this document since the release of
  &productnamereg; 11 SP3.
 </para>
 <para>This manual was updated on the following dates:</para>
 <!--list of xrefs, latest date sorted upmost-->
 <itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
   <para>
    <xref linkend="sec.deployment.docupdates.sle12_ga" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
   </para>
  </listitem>
 </itemizedlist>

 <sect1 id="sec.deployment.docupdates.sle12_ga">
  <title>September XX, 2014 (Initial Release of &productname; 12)</title>
  <variablelist>
   <!--list of general issues that apply to all books-->
   <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" 
    href="common_docupdates_general_i.xml"/>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.inst"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Completely re-wrote the chapter because of the new installation
	workflow. 
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	The installation routine now supports setting up multiple network
	devices during the installation (<ulink url="
	http://fate.suse.com/315680"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	The installation proposal contains a separate
	<filename>/home</filename> partition formatted with XFS (<ulink
	url="http://fate.suse.com/316637"/> and <ulink
	url="http://fate.suse.com/316624"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.y2.hw"/></term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	<xref linkend="sec.y2.hw.scan"/>: &yast; no longer supports parallel
	port scanners
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
